    "starRating": "FIVE",
    "comment": "Tuvimos un problema con el auto a 70 km de ahi. Nos fueron a buscar y nos acompañaron hasta un mecanico para que nos reparen la bomba de agua.\nFacundo el que manejaba la grua se quedo con nosotros y nos facilito todo lo que pudo. Impecable su ayuda.\nLa gente del ACA nos ofrecio habitaciones por si nos teniamos que quedar la noche sin importar haber reservado con tiempo. No hizo falta pero su predisposición estuvo.\nGracias\n\n(Translated by Google)\nWe had a car problem 70 km away. They picked us up and escorted us to a mechanic to have the water pump repaired.\nFacundo, the tow truck driver, stayed with us and provided everything he could. His help was impeccable.\nThe ACA staff offered us rooms in case we had to stay the night, even though we had booked ahead of time. It wasn\u0027t necessary, but their willingness was there.\nThank you.",
